                            <comment id="17790892" author="tilman" created="Wed, 29 Nov 2023 04:31:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tresf&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tresf&quot;&gt;tresf&lt;/a&gt; did you test the modification from the linked github PR? I just tried it, it makes no difference at 100% but it makes a difference at 50%. But maybe it makes a difference on MacOS for you?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17790900" author="tresf" created="Wed, 29 Nov 2023 05:17:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; thanks for testing.&#160; Since the linked PR is against trunk, the test example project had to be &lt;a href=&quot;https://pdfbox.apache.org/3.0/migration.html#use-loader-to-get-a-pdf-document&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;modified slightly&lt;/a&gt; to compile, but yes, it fixes the issue.&#160; Note, that the example project intentionally prints to a 4x6 PDF to reproduce the issue, which is roughly 50% of an A4/US Letter.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
